/19940504?_ga=1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 早前表示若收集到38000個公民提名就會參選特首的社民連梁國雄宣佈截至周五只收集到20000個提名，其結束收集提名行動並表明不尋求民主派選委支持他出選行政長官。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1555842&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1555842%26target%3D2&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ab3cc7d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1555842%26target%3D2&h=225f3ea8\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1555842&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170226/19940517?_ga=1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170226%2F19940517%3F_ga%3D1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4bc309e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170226%2F19940517%3F_ga%3D1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048&h=4582b2de\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170226/19940517?_ga=1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 警察員佐級協會發出嚴正聲明強調坊間團體「香港警察員佐級協會創建人暨退役同僚聯會」舉辦的一切活動一概與協會無關。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1555863&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1555863%26target%3D2&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3363c3a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1555863%26target%3D2&h=1ea72380\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1555863&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 英國外交及聯邦事務部日前向英國國會提交新一份「香港問題半年報告書」，總結指出一國兩制在多方面均運作良好，中國外交部及港府均回應指要求英方停止干預香港事務。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170226/00176_045.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F00176_045.html&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=81c4469f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170226/00176_045.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 就財政司司長官官邸以200萬元進行翻新工程一事，財政司司長陳茂波表示官邸只是進行基本修葺，並非豪裝，他又否認搬入官邸是預視自己可以留任。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00002/1488045625797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00002%2F1488045625797&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c5cd739d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170226%2Fs00002%2F1488045625797&h=c6a1fb78\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170226/s00002/1488045625797</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170226/00176_041.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170226%2F00176_041.html&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8752e047\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170226/00176_041.html</a> (東方日報) <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170226/19940427?_ga=1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170226%2F19940427%3F_ga%3D1.205012176.1316658954.1419942048&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d7b0bc4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170226%2F19940427%